From sfalcon at fhcrc.org  Sun Jan  7 03:23:38 2007
From: sfalcon at fhcrc.org (Seth Falcon)
Date: Sat, 06 Jan 2007 18:23:38 -0800
Subject: [Bioc-devel] Install subset of R package
